    "text": "Department of Energy and Nuclear Regulatory Commission Whistleblower Protection Act\n\nThis bill revises protections for the rights of whistleblowers of nuclear safety violations. Specifically, the bill clarifies that whistleblower protection rights may be enforced against any employers (e.g., the Department of Energy and the Nuclear Regulatory Commission)."
